description: Staxx Panwich, with its innovative selection of gourmet pancake sandwiches, is making its mark on the LA map!Taking their very own hand-mixed vegan batter, your favorite breakfast flavors, and the finest quality ingredients, this team is griddling up some deliciously sweet & savory panwiches. No matter the time of day, their menu will get your stomach rumbling. A few of the items you’ll find include the Breakfast Club (with a sunny side up egg, crisp bacon, and provolone) and The Minion (with tender corn flaked chicken, fresh tomato, arugula, and sriracha aioli). If your sweet tooth is calling the shots, you’re sure to just love the S’moreogasm (Oreo batter, chocolate, graham cracker, and marshmallow). For all this and much more, head out to Staxx and pamper your appetite with these sensational pancake creations.
name: Staxx Panwich
